## Description {#details}

Sample profile pseudo prober.

Insert pseudo probes for block sampling and value sampling.

Definition at line 74 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/transforms/include/llvm/transforms/ipo/sampleprofileprobe-h">SampleProfileProbe.h</a>.
